                  ornare nisl. Phasellus pede arcu, dapibus eu.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article>
        <header class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="text-dark-100 font-bold font-mono text-5xl">
            <span class="mr-3 font-normal text-primary-100">03</span>Button
          </h2>
        </header>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
